Put a full stop.
Not a question mark.

1563
01:56:13,291 --> 01:56:16,624
<i>[Not finished]</i>

1564
01:56:23,666 --> 01:56:27,666
Mr. Editor, don't write
his obituary yet.

1565
01:56:27,666 --> 01:56:29,582
My son will rise again!

1566
01:56:30,416 --> 01:56:33,374
