1569
01:56:43,041 --> 01:56:47,874
<i>A lousy editor writing me off
was unacceptable to dad.</i>

1570
01:56:48,541 --> 01:56:52,624
<i>He resolved to get my life
back on track.</i>

1571
01:56:52,791 --> 01:56:57,332
