1634
02:01:25,791 --> 02:01:28,957
I too, have a father.
He disapproves.

1635
02:01:31,041 --> 02:01:34,082
He approves when you meet
the gangs in Dubai?

1636
02:01:34,374 --> 02:01:37,124
Did I have a choice?
I was scared.

1637
02:01:39,499 --> 02:01:41,374
You ain't scared of me?

1638
